    Returns, Exchanges and Refunds
  </h1>
  <div class="rte">
    <h3><strong>We make returns and exchanges easy.</strong></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Buy with confidence, we offer a 99 day money back guarantee. Within <span>99</span> days of purchase, return your socks for a refund or exchange for a different size, no questions asked.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Our return policy lasts <span>99</span> days. If <span>99</span> days have gone by since your purchase, unfortunately, we can’t offer you a refund or exchange. If you are having a product issue, please email </span><a href="mailto:support@hollowsocks.com"><span style="font-weight: 400;">support@hollowsocks.com</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> for assistance. To complete your return, we require proof of purchase. Please note: we do not cover the shipping cost of returns.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you need to make a return or exchange within the <span>99</span> day window, please visit <a href="https://hollowsocks.com/apps/redo/account">https://hollowsocks.com/apps/redo/account</a></span><a href="mailto:support@hollowsocks.com"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> to get started.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Once your return is received and inspected, we will process the refund or exchange. If receiving a refund, a credit will automatically be applied to your original method of payment, and may take 5-7 business days to appear in your account. If exchanging for a different product, the new product will be shipped once the product being exchanged is received by our team. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you have a problem, we will handle it. Just send an email to </span><a href="mailto:support@hollowsocks.com"><span style="font-weight: 400;">support@hollowsocks.com</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">*Refunds are issued to your original form of payment only. </span></p>
  </div>
